{"tid":1545131,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【國際反支戰線】我哋要引用各國革命事蹟去做eye-catching嘅文宣！","createTime":"2019-09-05T21:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T14:12:16.000Z","uid":108502,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"77d47a91c13a2831e50c980ae094ed116b71bc2c","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:23:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1544231/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1544231/page/1</a><br />\n正如上一個post提到<br />\n有位手足引用咗巴西獨立革命嘅格言：Independ&ecirc;ncia ou Morte （不獨立毋寧死）就connect咗一班巴西人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDn-HpOUUAABiQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEDn-HpOUUAABiQB.jpg&h=688a02aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=79d69bfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&h=e399dacc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>我哋應該將依位手足嘅策略發揚光大<br />\n就係要用唔同方法，包括banner，海報，塗鴉等等<br />\n用最低成本獲得世界各國嘅留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗咗幾個熱血嘅革命slogan，唔知遲下會唔會遍地開花喺我哋嘅街頭見返呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Vivre Libre ou Mourir (Live Free or Die 不自由毋寧死) <br />\nVive la R&eacute;volution! (Long live the Revolution! 革命萬歲！)</span></span><br />\n講起革命，就梗係會諗到法國大革命啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依兩句slogan比較通用，唔似自由平等博愛咁，一講起就一定諗起法國<br />\n所以非常適合出現喺香港街頭！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Слава Україні! Героям слава! (Glory to Ukraine! Glory to Heroes! 烏克蘭萬歲！榮耀歸於英雄！) </span></span><br />\n烏克蘭革命一直都為我哋帶嚟啟發，而佢哋嘅口號亦非常熱血！<br />\n第一句烏克蘭萬歲當然唔係太適合，但係Героям слава，榮耀歸於英雄<br />\n講比我哋嘅義士，以及為我哋死諫嘅烈士<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（但真係唔好再自殺）</span>聽，係最適合不過！<br />\n西里爾字母睇落好似外星文咁，但依句其實唔難寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage1a.censor.net/images/7/a/2/5/7a25cb70364f1f14bc79eee571d629fd/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage1a.censor.net%2Fimages%2F7%2Fa%2F2%2F5%2F7a25cb70364f1f14bc79eee571d629fd%2Foriginal.jpg&h=d22b526a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbtw曾經睇live見過有巴打舉烏克蘭國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知會唔會有人學埋烏克蘭國歌呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就學咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家都嚟聽下！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNl5HyhhWwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFNl5HyhhWwg&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=38d517f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNl5HyhhWwg</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個好值得connect嘅，就係各國駐港領事<br />\n例如2014年嘅時候，波蘭駐港領事都曾經接受訪問，將雨傘同自己參與東歐劇變嘅經歷連繫 (<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%23%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%23&amp;suid=3613491473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Ffeatures%2Farticle%3Fq%3D%2523%25E9%25A0%2598%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2588%2597%2523%26suid%3D3613491473&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=61d65113\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%23%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%23&amp;suid=3613491473</a>)<br />\n所以如果我哋引用一啲有駐港領事館嘅國家嘅歷史，就好有機會等到迴響！<br />\n例如關於波蘭可以引用我哋都有聽過嘅波蘭團結工會嘅歷史：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Nie ma wolności bez Solidarności (There is no freedom without solidarity 團結才會自由) -</span></span><br />\n依句口號喺波蘭嘅語境當然係為團結工會爭取支持<br />\n但對我哋嚟講，係完全切合『不分化，不割蓆』嘅原則 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個可以嘗試connect嘅領事就梗係抽水專家德國啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如黃之鋒同默克爾講你來自東德，你也曾經歷極權統治<br />\n我哋都可以remind下德國人反抗極權嘅歷史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Wir sind das Volk! (We are the people! 我們是人民！)</span></span><br />\n一方面表達權力歸於人民嘅目標<br />\n另一方面，就係要同世界講，我哋嘅抗爭係代表民意嘅！<br />\n<br />\n大家都可以再諗下有冇其他適合嘅motto <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但要記住一啲原則：<br />\n1. 儘量唔好用共產革命嘅口號啦，即使有啲口號係幾熱血，但對外國嚟講我哋就係對抗緊Chinese communist，無端端有共產嘢會有啲奇怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 儘量揀返公認係印象良好嘅革命，反例係中東嘅革命，因為佢哋嘅結局暫時仲係不幸，引用佢哋就會唔係咁好了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 儘量用一啲正面嘅口號，而唔係一啲反面，有攻擊性嘅口號，廢事唔小心得罪人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如講烏克蘭，用榮耀歸於英雄就fit晒，而用Путін, хуйло<br />\n（普京，傻閪）<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（雖然好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span> 就唔好了，因為會得罪俄羅斯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然都好難connect到俄佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/46/Anti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%2C_May_2014.jpg/200px-Anti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%2C_May_2014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F46%2FAnti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%252C_May_2014.jpg%2F200px-Anti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%252C_May_2014.jpg&h=0c3915c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>4. 好重要！一定要串啱字！另外如果人哋嘅語言有啲變音符號，都儘量寫埋佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要尊重返人哋嘅語言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各位巴打，仲有唔夠一個月就到十一嘅大日子<br />\n我哋要好好準備返一份大禮俾對家啊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">全世界嘅風向，就由連登仔引領！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d5a9594543bb68ea544672ffef3bf9dc32512801","tid":1545131,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:24:04.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82a57a590f3a812278906d12cb67cd6bec712651","tid":1545131,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n907 機場攻略正式出爐，唔使再驚大逃走！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544251</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=e2f8fd59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"19e56bad7edc5aa72eaffaef245477345a890e40","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:25:09.000Z","msg":"一齊推爆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a370a5ba4dfb67c71a031f3c09051c9656c5abf","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbf5f92979c57e8165a8e08ce0d870d0144bad6","tid":1545131,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:34:46.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭萬歲改做香港萬歲 後面照跟得唔得"},{"pid":"1c45f907f4770952dd9b6a97de6240312b693509","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fbf5f92979c57e8165a8e08ce0d870d0144bad6","tid":1545131,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:34:46.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭萬歲改做香港萬歲 後面照跟得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:36:53.000Z","msg":"咁就Слава Гонконгу<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f06376596356abefea8fc75785e4a0d9bea1b5","tid":1545131,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce05958c1f34bf44691f4e928fb38be33eb47030","tid":1545131,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7379534cffd507ab2cc1ac36751bf254821c624","tid":1545131,"uid":205862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:51:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"766d158809ccc6df306aa4e4a895fb8b20ba55d3","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:57:36.000Z","msg":"推到日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52754659508fdd398fbdd9dd695fc7059cb2a616","tid":1545131,"uid":310716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d47a91c13a2831e50c980ae094ed116b71bc2c","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:23:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1544231/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1544231/page/1</a><br />\n正如上一個post提到<br />\n有位手足引用咗巴西獨立革命嘅格言：Independ&ecirc;ncia ou Morte （不獨立毋寧死）就connect咗一班巴西人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDn-HpOUUAABiQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEDn-HpOUUAABiQB.jpg&h=688a02aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=79d69bfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ferinhale%2Fstatus%2F1169244995095674882&h=e399dacc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/erinhale/status/1169244995095674882</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>我哋應該將依位手足嘅策略發揚光大<br />\n就係要用唔同方法，包括banner，海報，塗鴉等等<br />\n用最低成本獲得世界各國嘅留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗咗幾個熱血嘅革命slogan，唔知遲下會唔會遍地開花喺我哋嘅街頭見返呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Vivre Libre ou Mourir (Live Free or Die 不自由毋寧死) <br />\nVive la R&eacute;volution! (Long live the Revolution! 革命萬歲！)</span></span><br />\n講起革命，就梗係會諗到法國大革命啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依兩句slogan比較通用，唔似自由平等博愛咁，一講起就一定諗起法國<br />\n所以非常適合出現喺香港街頭！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Слава Україні! Героям слава! (Glory to Ukraine! Glory to Heroes! 烏克蘭萬歲！榮耀歸於英雄！) </span></span><br />\n烏克蘭革命一直都為我哋帶嚟啟發，而佢哋嘅口號亦非常熱血！<br />\n第一句烏克蘭萬歲當然唔係太適合，但係Героям слава，榮耀歸於英雄<br />\n講比我哋嘅義士，以及為我哋死諫嘅烈士<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（但真係唔好再自殺）</span>聽，係最適合不過！<br />\n西里爾字母睇落好似外星文咁，但依句其實唔難寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage1a.censor.net/images/7/a/2/5/7a25cb70364f1f14bc79eee571d629fd/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage1a.censor.net%2Fimages%2F7%2Fa%2F2%2F5%2F7a25cb70364f1f14bc79eee571d629fd%2Foriginal.jpg&h=d22b526a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbtw曾經睇live見過有巴打舉烏克蘭國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知會唔會有人學埋烏克蘭國歌呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就學咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家都嚟聽下！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNl5HyhhWwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFNl5HyhhWwg&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=38d517f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNl5HyhhWwg</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個好值得connect嘅，就係各國駐港領事<br />\n例如2014年嘅時候，波蘭駐港領事都曾經接受訪問，將雨傘同自己參與東歐劇變嘅經歷連繫 (<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%23%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%23&amp;suid=3613491473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Ffeatures%2Farticle%3Fq%3D%2523%25E9%25A0%2598%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2588%2597%2523%26suid%3D3613491473&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=61d65113\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/features/article?q=%23%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%23&amp;suid=3613491473</a>)<br />\n所以如果我哋引用一啲有駐港領事館嘅國家嘅歷史，就好有機會等到迴響！<br />\n例如關於波蘭可以引用我哋都有聽過嘅波蘭團結工會嘅歷史：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Nie ma wolności bez Solidarności (There is no freedom without solidarity 團結才會自由) -</span></span><br />\n依句口號喺波蘭嘅語境當然係為團結工會爭取支持<br />\n但對我哋嚟講，係完全切合『不分化，不割蓆』嘅原則 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個可以嘗試connect嘅領事就梗係抽水專家德國啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如黃之鋒同默克爾講你來自東德，你也曾經歷極權統治<br />\n我哋都可以remind下德國人反抗極權嘅歷史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Wir sind das Volk! (We are the people! 我們是人民！)</span></span><br />\n一方面表達權力歸於人民嘅目標<br />\n另一方面，就係要同世界講，我哋嘅抗爭係代表民意嘅！<br />\n<br />\n大家都可以再諗下有冇其他適合嘅motto <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但要記住一啲原則：<br />\n1. 儘量唔好用共產革命嘅口號啦，即使有啲口號係幾熱血，但對外國嚟講我哋就係對抗緊Chinese communist，無端端有共產嘢會有啲奇怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 儘量揀返公認係印象良好嘅革命，反例係中東嘅革命，因為佢哋嘅結局暫時仲係不幸，引用佢哋就會唔係咁好了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 儘量用一啲正面嘅口號，而唔係一啲反面，有攻擊性嘅口號，廢事唔小心得罪人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如講烏克蘭，用榮耀歸於英雄就fit晒，而用Путін, хуйло<br />\n（普京，傻閪）<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（雖然好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span> 就唔好了，因為會得罪俄羅斯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然都好難connect到俄佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/46/Anti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%2C_May_2014.jpg/200px-Anti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%2C_May_2014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F46%2FAnti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%252C_May_2014.jpg%2F200px-Anti-Putin_graffiti_in_Luhansk%252C_May_2014.jpg&h=0c3915c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>4. 好重要！一定要串啱字！另外如果人哋嘅語言有啲變音符號，都儘量寫埋佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要尊重返人哋嘅語言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各位巴打，仲有唔夠一個月就到十一嘅大日子<br />\n我哋要好好準備返一份大禮俾對家啊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">全世界嘅風向，就由連登仔引領！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:58:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">9月8日差你一個！<br />\n幫美國推法案 迫香港2020年普選！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Axu5DVG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxu5DVG.jpg&h=396a48de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qaTNO2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qaTNO2.jpg&h=c1e7dea9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49LTNO3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49LTNO3.jpg&h=103c633c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQKxiVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQKxiVK.jpg&h=e7d8cceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsPQP2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsPQP2q.jpg&h=d7d4ae1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SADYYVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSADYYVM.jpg&h=a8883fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZFDYVN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZFDYVN.jpg&h=328bd861&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g86oqAO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg86oqAO.jpg&h=f93377ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0374b2d9c7e49f48cad9d88c8c5437f90a995527","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07462fac51cfd06386e31f019489aa73718d9c00","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e44816e76bbac145eb6b6f75e43f1ca432acd8","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6444a8eba0c9e2d30f17f9b52aecdd920ecf52","tid":1545131,"uid":312833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:34:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#FreeUyghur</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Add this and others to your twitter<br />\nUse English as far as possible</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">But don't follow some radical groups<br />\nDon't use any of their resources.<br />\nDon't connect to any organisation in the banner.<br />\nThis is only to arouse international attention to Hong Kong <br />\nMust be very careful with this so as not to give an excuse for #chinazi to intervene.</span>"},{"pid":"c75f90b6e4610cb5c8f527c73feee99793fb6f74","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:48:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b92976dc908658b91f91c1872920434a13a1e0a2","tid":1545131,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fca8db58150686a1fc1da5011708fb3f4ffd1a","tid":1545131,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e44816e76bbac145eb6b6f75e43f1ca432acd8","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W0rjHeB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW0rjHeB.jpg&h=9a2aaf52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足們:<br />\n我整咗個Butterfly分解教學比大家。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYoutube片: <a href=\"http://shorturl.at/aBNY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshorturl.at%2FaBNY4&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=60e560ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://shorturl.at/aBNY4</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一方有難</span>  針<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">  八方支援</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山</span>  爆</strong>   <span style=\"color: gold;\">  各自努力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span>  黨<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">  時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求</span>  鐵</strong>   <span style=\"color: gold;\">  缺一不可!</span>"},{"pid":"5c9ab69a3c75ea6c26035a5b6e7b8d410dce9dbc","tid":1545131,"uid":310805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:07:16.000Z","msg":"Push push push<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, for the people!!!"},{"pid":"7e8052e7be30593ec769d1c77633269d8389d3c5","tid":1545131,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548fa9484ad4f2f0d4aab6fdc50a1468e70e956c","tid":1545131,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478a347bc0dd05e98f5b9701b4e154038df9a5fa","tid":1545131,"uid":286795,"li